<HTML>
<HEAD><TITLE>DCCA:  Energy, Coal & Recycling Programs -- Energy</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" TEXT="#004080" LINK="#004080" VLINK="#8080C0" ALINK="#8080C0">

<img src="/dcca/graph/logosm.jpg" alt="DCCA Logo" width=165 height=82 align=left>
<img src="/dcca/graph/cbar.gif" width=410 height=4><p>
<h3>
Department of Commerce & Community Affairs<p>
</h3>
<img src="/dcca/graph/cbar.gif" width=410 height=4><p>
<font size=+3>Energy, Coal & Recycling Programs</font>
<br clear=right>
<hr>


<img src="../graph/enr/recycle.jpg" width=193 height=190 hspace=10 vspace=10 align=left>
<h3 align=center>
Recycling & Waste Reduction<br>
Reduce * Reuse * Recycle
</h3>


The Illinois Solid Waste Management Act (415ILCS 20/1 et seq.) authorizes the Department of Commerce and Community Affairs (DCCA) to promote alternative means of managing solid waste with the goal of reducing reliance on land disposal.<p>

Through the Bureaus of Energy and Recycling, DCCA has established an array of programs to provide funding to qualified applicants for project directly related to the goals of the Solid Waste Management Act.  All programs, except the Used Tire Recovery Program, are funded with DCCA's share of the $0.45 per cubic yard tipping fee surcharge imposed on all municipal waste landfilled in Illinois.  The Used Tire Recovery Program is funded with DCCA's share of the $1.00 surcharge on he sale of each new tire in Illinois.  These programs encourage the implementation of waste reduction, recycling, energy recovery, and composting methods as alternative to conventional landfill disposal.  The goals of these DCCA programs and services are to divert large volumes of waste from landfills or incinerator disposal and to foster recycling endeavors in Illinois.<p>

<hr>
<H3>
<A HREF="../files/enr/remarket.htm"> Recycling Market Development Program</A><BR>
<A HREF="../files/enr/regrant.htm"> Illinois Recycling Grants Program</A><BR>
<A HREF="../files/enr/techdemo.htm"> Technologies & Practices Demonstration Program</A><BR>
<A HREF="../files/enr/tires.htm"> Illinois Used Tire Program</A><BR>
<A HREF="../files/enr/school.htm"> School Education Program</A><BR>
<A HREF="../files/enr/solwaste.htm"> Solid Waste Management Research Program</A><BR>
<A HREF="../files/enr/icap.htm"> Illinois College Assistance Program for Recycling (ICAP)</A><BR>
</H3>

<HR>
<STRONG>| <A HREF="http://www.ilcommerce.com">DCCA Home Page</A> | <A HREF="enr.htm"> Energy, Coal & Recycling</A> |</STRONG>
</BODY>
</HTML>
