<h3 align=center>Illinois Department of Commerce & Community Affairs</h3>
<center><img src="../../graph/dccalog3.jpg" alt="DCCA Logo" width=275 height=137></center>

<hr>

<img src="../../graph/city.gif" width=267 height=80 align=left>
<img src="../../graph/barn.gif" width=229 height=80 align=right>
<br clear=all>
<hr>

<h2 align=center>Welcome to the Illinois Community Profiles Database</h2>
<p>This database contains statistical and demographic information provided by each participating community in Illinois.
<p>We hope that you find this service helpful in planning your next expansion or relocation.  Please <A HREF="mailto:tom.hamrick@accessil.com"><strong>write us</strong></A> on ways that we can help you in selecting Illinois . . . a great state that keeps getting better!
<address>
<p>Dennis R. Whetstone,
<br>Director
</address>
<hr>


<ul type=square>
<li><strong><a href="#StartTheForm">Search the database for a community.</a></strong>
<p>
<li><a href="http://www.ilcommerce.com/files/CommunityProfiles/WhatIsCommunityProfiles.htm">What is the Illinois Community Profiles program?</a>
<li>How to <a href="http://www.ilcommerce.com/files/CommunityProfiles/HowToAddCommunity.htm">Add Your Community</a> to the database.
<li><a href="../commlink.htm"> Links to Illinois Communities</a>
</ul>


<hr>
<A NAME="StartTheForm"><h2 align=center>Community Profiles Region Search</h2>
<a href="/dcca/graph/commprofreg.map"><img src="/DCCA/Graph/CommProfRegions.gif" alt="Image Map" border=0 ismap align=left></a>
<p>Choose a region from the map at the left for a list of all Communities in that region.
<p><strong>NOTE:</strong> There is also a <a href="#Form1"><em>search form available.</em></a>
<br clear=all>


<hr>
<A NAME="Form1"><h2 align=center>Community Profiles Search Form</h2></A>
<p>Enter your parameters below to search for Communities.  If you leave all parameters at their default, you will get a list of all communities.
<p>
<form method="POST" action="/Progs/CommProfList.exe">
<pre>Select Communities with population  <select name="PopulationChoice"><option>All<option>Over<option>Under</select>:   <input name="Population" type="TEXT" value="0" size="12"> people<br></pre>


<hr>
<input name="EnterprizeZoneOnly" type="CHECKBOX" value="0"> Only Communities with an <a href="http://www.ilcommerce.com/files/commasst/eprise.htm"> Enterprise Zone</a>?<br>
<input name="FgnTdZoneOnly" type="CHECKBOX" value="0"> Only Communities with a Foreign Trade Zone?<br>
<input name="TIFZoneOnly" type="CHECKBOX" value="0"> Only Communities with a <a href="http://www.ilcommerce.com/files/taxinc2.htm"> Tax Increment Financing (TIF) Zone</a>?<br>
<hr>
<pre><input type=submit>   <input type=reset></pre>
</form>



