<HEAD><TITLE>DCCA: Proposed Rules - December 2, 1996</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" TEXT="#000080" LINK="#000080" VLINK="#8080C0" ALINK="#8080C0">

<img src="/dcca/graph/logosm.jpg" alt="DCCA Logo" width=165 height=82 align=left>
<img src="/dcca/graph/cbar.gif" width=410 height=4><p>
<h3>
Department of Commerce & Community Affairs<p>
</h3>
<img src="/dcca/graph/cbar.gif" width=410 height=4><p>
<font size=+3>Proposed Rules</font>
<hr>

<CENTER>
The proposed rules marked with an * are of particular interest to small
business and the department specifically requests comments on those issues.
Comments on any rule are encouraged.<P>
</CENTER>
<HR>
<h3 align=center>
Illinois Register<BR>
December 2, 1996
</h3>
<hr>

<strong>* NOTICE OF PUBLIC HEARING</strong> - Department of Public Health proposed rules titled "Structural Pest Control Code", published November 15, 1996.  Hearing December 10 from 1:30p to 3:30p at DPH, First Floor Training Room, 525 W. Jefferson St., Springfield.<p>

<hr>
<h4>ILLINOIS COMMUNITY COLLEGE BOARD</h4>

<strong><em>Administration of the Illinois Public Community College Act</em></strong> - Allows ICCB funding for courses that meet the "Guidelines for Community College Courses Offered in Secondary Schools."<p>

<hr>
<h4>DEPARTMENT OF NATURAL RESOURCES</h4>

<strong><em>Illinois List of Endangered and Threatened Fauna</em></strong> - Removes Cooper's Hawk.<p>

<strong><em>The Taking of Wild Turkeys</em></strong> - Spring Season - Opens several counties and six new state-owned areas to wild turkey hunting.<p>

<hr>
<h4>ILLINOIS RACING BOARD</h4>

<strong><em>Horse Health</em></strong> - Reorganizes all rules regarding horse health applicable to harness and thoroughbred racing.  (New)<p>

<strong><em>Medication</em></strong> -  As above relative to medications.  Adds six medications to the permitted foreign substances list.  New Provisions for administration of furosemide and penalties for excessive amounts.  (New)<p>

<strong><em>Medication</em></strong> - Repeal replaced by above.<p>

<strong><em>PPT</em></strong> - Establishes a PPT wager which combines two perfectas and one trifecta into a single wager.  (New)<p>

<hr>
<h4>DEPARTMENT OF REHABILITATION SERVICES</h4>

<strong><em>Customer Financial Participation</em></strong> - Revises customer financial participation of the cost of the vocational rehab services.  Makes the Standard Budget Allowances and rate of participation more fair and equitable for all individuals seeking services.  Parental participation has been revised to match the federal guidelines for student financial assistance. <p>

<HR>
<STRONG>| <A HREF="/dcca/home.htm">DCCA Home Page</A> | <A HREF="/dcca/menus/regflex.htm"> Regulatory Flexibility</A> | <A HREF="../../menus/rfprop.htm"> Proposed Rules</A> |</STRONG>
</BODY>
