<h3 align=center>
Illinois Register<BR>
November 8, 1996
</h3>
<hr>

<h4>DEPARTMENT OF AGRICULTURE</h4>

<strong><em>Fairs Operating Under the Agricultural Fair Act</em></strong> - Relative to county fair associations and agricultural societies amending exhibitors requirements, cost determinations, livestock dismissal, classifications and submittal of information.<p>

<hr>
<h4>DEPARTMENT OF ALCOHOLISM AND SUBSTANCE ABUSE</h4>

<strong><em>Subacute Alcoholism and Substance Abuse Treatment Services</em></strong> - Consolidates enrollment, certification and recertification sections into one to conform with Part 2060.<p>

<hr>
<h4>ILLINOIS COMMUNITY COLLEGE BOARD</h4>

<strong><em>Administration of the Illinois Public Community College Act</em></strong> - Provides districts with leased facilities more flexibility in funding alterations or repairs.<p>

<hr>
<h4>DEPARTMENT OF INSURANCE</h4>

<strong><em>Prior Notification of Dividends on Common Stock and Other Distributions</em></strong> - Requires companies submitting a filing relating to issuance of extraordinary dividend to provide the Department with a calculation of its risk based capital.<p>

<hr>
<h4>TEACHERS' RETIREMENT SYSTEM OF THE STATE OF ILLINOIS</h4>

<strong><em>The Administration and Operation of the Teachers' Retirement System</em></strong> - Amendments and new sections relative to retiring teachers.<p>

<hr>
<h4>DEPARTMENT OF TRANSPORTATION</h4>

<strong><em>Aviation Safety</em></strong> - Clarifies that emergency medical flights are allowed at hospital RLA (restricted landing area) heliports.<p>


