<HEAD><TITLE>First Stop: Regulation of Infectious Diseases among Animals</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" TEXT="#004080" LINK="#004080" VLINK="#0080C0" ALINK="#0080C0">

<img src="/dcca/graph/fs/fslogosm.gif" alt="First Stop Logo" width=171 height=120 align=left>
<h3 align=center>Department of Commerce & Community Affairs
<hr>
First Stop Business Information Center<br>
Business Requirement
</h3>
<hr>
<br clear=all>

<H3>I.  Business Requirement Profile:</H3>
<DL><DD>
Regulation of Infectious Diseases among Animals
</DD></DL>

<HR>
<H3>II.  Agency:</H3>
<DL><DD>
Illinois Department of Agriculture<BR>
Bureau of Animal Health<BR>
P.O. Box 19281<BR>
Springfield, IL 62794-9281<BR>
(217) 782-4944<BR>
</DD></DL>

<HR>
<H3>III. Statute:</H3>
<DL><DD>
	510 Illinois Compiled Statutes 50/1 et seq.<BR>
	Illinois Diseased Animals Act<BR>
	Illinois Equine Infections Anemia  Control Act<BR>
	Illinois Bovine Brucellosis Eradication Act<BR>
	Illinois Bovine Tuberculosis Eradication Act<BR>
	Illinois Swine Disease Control and Eradication Act<BR>
	Swine Brucellosis Eradication Act<BR>
	Illinois Pseudorabies Control Act<BR>
	Trichinosis Control Act<BR>
	Poultry Inspection Act<BR>
	Bees and Apiaries Act (Beekeepers Act)<BR>
</DD></DL>

<HR>
<H3>IV.  Requirement Description:</H3>
<DL><DD>
These Acts apply to the production of animals.  The  Department investigates all cases or alleged cases of contagious and infectious diseases among animals within the State and provides for the suppression, prevention, and extirpation of infectious and contagious animal diseases. The Department may quarantine or order the slaughter or destruction of diseases animals.  Producers may not knowingly remove, transport or sell diseased animals.  Producers must notify the Illinois Department of Agriculture of any diseased animals.  Producers must use reasonable means to prevent the spread of contagious or infectious diseases.  Violations of the Act may result in fines from $50 to $1,000.  
</DD></DL>

<HR>
<H3>V.  Approval Process:</H3>
<DL><DD>
N/A
</DD></DL>

<HR>
<H3>VI.  Pre-Requisites, Co-Requisites & Post-Requisites:</H3>
<DL><DD>
N/A
</DD></DL>

<HR>
<H3>VII.  Fees:  </H3>
<DL><DD>
N/A
</DD></DL>

