<HTML>
<HEAD><TITLE>First Stop: Illinois Six Day Work Week Law  </TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" TEXT="#004080" LINK="#004080" VLINK="#0080C0" ALINK="#0080C0">

<img src="/dcca/graph/fs/fslogosm.gif" alt="First Stop Logo" width=171 height=120 align=left>
<h3 align=center>Department of Commerce & Community Affairs
<hr>
First Stop Business Information Center<br>
Business Requirement
</h3>
<hr>
<br clear=all>

<H3>I.	Business Requirement Profile:</H3>
<DL><DD>
Illinois Six Day Work Week Law  
</DD></DL>

<HR>
<H3>II.	Agency:</H3>
<DL><DD>
Department of Labor<BR>
Fair Labor Standards Division<BR>
160 N. LaSalle<BR>
Chicago, IL 60601<BR>
(312) 793-2804<BR>
</DD></DL>

<HR>
<H3>III.	Statute:</H3>
<DL><DD>
820 Illinois Compiled Statutes 140/1.
</DD></DL>

<HR>
<H3>IV.	Requirement Description:</H3>
<DL><DD>
The Law requires all employers to provide one day off in every calendar week and to provide a meal break of 20 minutes or longer to employees working 7 1/2 hours or more.<P>
</DD></DL>

<HR>
<H3>V.	Approval Process:</H3>
<DL><DD>
Employers may request a Permit to depart from the terms of the Law. The Department will mail written approval or denial of requests  to depart from the terms of the Law. Employers may request relief by telephone, but must promptly submit the request in writing to the Department. Permits for relief during the first eight weeks of a calendar year will be granted by the Director of the Department. Permits for relief for periods of time in excess of eight weeks may require greater justification.<P>
</DD></DL>

<HR>
<H3>VI.	Pre-Requisites, Co-Requisites & Post-Requisites:</H3>
<DL><DD>
An employer must receive written approval from the Department  before an employee may work seven days in a calendar week. In such cases, employees must be allowed to volunteer to work seven days in a calendar week. Employers must maintain records to verify meal breaks, and the permits issued by the  agency. Records must be kept available for inspection by the Department for three years.<P>
</DD></DL>

<HR>
<H3>VII.	Fees:</H3>
<DL><DD>
None.
</DD></DL>


<HR>
<STRONG>| <a href="/dcca/home.htm">DCCA Home Page</a> | <A HREF="/dcca/menus/fsm1.htm">First Stop</a> | <A HREF="/dcca/menus/fsbr.htm">Business Requirements</a> |</STRONG>

